#title "K054539 Konami Advanced PCM Example"
#description "Konami K054539 advanced PCM chip with ADPCM"

$AdvancedPcm1=K054539@1
$AdvancedPcm2=K054539@2

* K054539 Channel 1
@AdvancedPcm1
@BANK0 @LOOP1
t120 l8
o5 c4 d4 e4 f4 | g4 a4 b4 >c4

* K054539 Channel 2
@AdvancedPcm2
@BANK1
t120 l4
o4 c c | g g | a a | f f
